text: Interconnect User Part (IUP) is a national specific Signaling System 7 protocol for interconnect between public telephone networks in the United Kingdom. This protocol was formerly known as BTNUP. It is specified in document PNO-ISC/SPEC/006 which is published by the NICC as ND1006:2007/05. Category:Signaling System 7 Category:Integrated Services Digital Network
title: Interconnect User Part
